WEBVTT

00:00:00.822 --> 00:00:03.617
ven ir zent ongekum- in BERGEN BELSEN.

00:00:01.362 --> 00:00:07.632
den, di BERGEN BELSEN m'iz ongekum- iz geven zeyer nisht keyn normale badingungen

00:00:07.632 --> 00:00:12.112
vos iz di khaos shoyn geven. di daytshn hobn nisht gekent dos bahershn afile.

00:00:12.195 --> 00:00:14.529
zeyer a sakh meysim zenen gelign

00:00:14.529 --> 00:00:18.706
un afile m'iz arayngan in lazaret, derman ikh mikh a meydl fun Lodzh

00:00:18.706 --> 00:00:20.761
a dayen's a eynikl

00:00:20.768 --> 00:00:25.419
iz gelign tsvishn di toyte. m'hot nisht gevust ver s'iz toyt un ver s'iz lebedik.

00:00:25.543 --> 00:00:28.156
s'iz geven sh- shreklekh tsu kukn

00:00:28.156 --> 00:00:29.216
dem bild

00:00:29.273 --> 00:00:31.058
fun BERGEN BELSEN.

00:00:31.058 --> 00:00:35.375
iz take a shvester fun dem meydl, lebt do in BNEI BRAK.

00:00:36.613 --> 00:00:38.365
in droysn

00:00:38.365 --> 00:00:43.678
yeder hot zikh gevolt rateven. s'iz nisht geven mit vos. s'iz nisht geven vu tsu nemen epes.

00:00:43.701 --> 00:00:46.361
s'iz ales gevezn a khaos.

00:00:46.603 --> 00:00:50.103
un m'hot gefilt az s'geyt vern di bafrayung, vayl

00:00:50.103 --> 00:00:53.503
poshet di bombardatsyes. m'hot zikh gefreyt fun eyn zayt az

00:00:53.503 --> 00:00:54.692
me bombardirt

00:00:54.692 --> 00:00:56.587
az s'kumt tsu ende.

00:00:56.712 --> 00:01:00.185
ober di badingungen zenen gevezn shreklekh.

00:01:00.185 --> 00:01:02.105
shreklekh f-

00:01:02.635 --> 00:01:05.616
arum un arum, di mentshn ontsukukn.

00:01:05.723 --> 00:01:06.800
s'iz geve-

00:01:06.800 --> 00:01:07.893
a pakhed.

00:01:08.052 --> 00:01:12.973
un vi iz dos az s'iz geven azoy fil mentshn dort? me hot gebrengt fun iberol?

00:01:12.422 --> 00:01:15.875
vos iz gevezn, m'hot gebrengt, m'hot arayngeshikt fun iberal

00:01:16.033 --> 00:01:19.554
hot men tsugeshikt nokh BERGEN BELSEN, vayl loyt vi zi iz

00:01:19.712 --> 00:01:24.611
s- ikh hob gehert un azoy ve s- s'hot gezolt zayn, hobn zey gevolt

00:01:24.611 --> 00:01:29.083
az s'zol gornisht blaybn, s'zol nisht iberik blaybn. zey hobn gezen az s'geyt tsu ende

00:01:29.083 --> 00:01:31.653
hobn zey gevolt az di ale lagern zoln

00:01:31.727 --> 00:01:36.226
oysgemekt ve- opgemekt vern, me zol gefinen nor meysim.

00:01:36.334 --> 00:01:39.804
az s'zol nisht zayn keyn eydes vos dos iz alts gevezn.

00:01:41.127 --> 00:01:43.112
mh dos iz

00:01:45.480 --> 00:01:49.220
un di daytshn zaynen nokh geven dort un nisht anklofn?

00:01:49.193 --> 00:01:52.544
n- a teyl efsher zenen antlofn. undz hot men dos nisht gezen.

00:01:52.544 --> 00:01:56.004
dos zenen di vos zey hobn undz gehitn zenen gevezn.

00:01:55.048 --> 00:01:56.864
zenen gevezn.

00:01:56.004 --> 00:01:58.594
yo, un zenen nokh geven gants genug shtreng.

00:01:58.930 --> 00:02:00.257
m'hot moyre gehat.

00:02:00.364 --> 00:02:03.108
m'hot moyre gehat, m'iz gevezn

00:02:02.372 --> 00:02:06.568
ets hots, m'hot enk gegebn tsu arbetn epes? gornisht?

00:02:04.920 --> 00:02:10.584
neyn, dos iz gevezn ales shoyn vild un on a, on a shum TOCHNIT.

00:02:11.130 --> 00:02:15.629
nisht keyn arbet un nisht, nisht tsu esn normal, gornisht. gornisht iz geven normal.

00:02:16.952 --> 00:02:21.721
un vi azoy hot ets, fun vos hot ets gelebt demolts di por teg? gornisht?

00:02:19.956 --> 00:02:24.590
gornisht. s'iz, az s'iz vi vilde mentshn in, in a, in a feld.

00:02:27.060 --> 00:02:30.598
dos iz nisht keyn normale badingungen iber hoypt geven.

00:02:30.638 --> 00:02:34.699
un mit di kuzine zent ir geven di gantse tsayt?

00:02:33.878 --> 00:02:35.407
mit mayn NICHTE.

00:02:34.907 --> 00:02:36.875
mit di NICHTE, yo, UNK.

00:02:35.970 --> 00:02:39.744
yo, bin ikh ⟨mit⟩ di gantse tsayt biz nokh di bafrayung.

00:02:40.189 --> 00:02:41.263
un

00:02:40.324 --> 00:02:45.043
ir kent bashraybn di bafrayung, vi, vi azoy dos iz tsugegangen?

00:02:43.159 --> 00:02:48.471
di bafrayung iz, i- i- farshidene aktsyes iz geven. di mentshn zenen aroysgelofn.

00:02:48.471 --> 00:02:52.704
eyner hot geshrign oyf di daytshn. eyner iz tsugegan aropgenumen zeygerlekh fun dem.

00:02:53.082 --> 00:02:56.445
ikh bin nisht aroysgegan. ikh bin geblibn in blok zitsn

00:02:56.445 --> 00:02:59.015
vayl denstmolt iz gevezn far mir

00:02:59.342 --> 00:03:02.638
dos iz di ende. m'vet zen vos vet vayter zayn.

00:03:02.638 --> 00:03:04.114
m'hot alts gemeynt. m'hot

00:03:04.114 --> 00:03:06.857
tsurik bakumen di gantse mishpokhe tsurikkumen.

00:03:06.857 --> 00:03:10.721
dos iz gevezn der ershter aktsye, un der tsveyter aktsye

00:03:07.948 --> 00:03:10.608
ir hot gemeynt di mishpokhe

00:03:10.721 --> 00:03:16.172
m'hot ongehoybn listn tsu nokhkukn, vu s'iz Horovitses, vu s'iz di mishpokhe.

00:03:16.172 --> 00:03:17.190
ober

00:03:17.382 --> 00:03:21.443
