00:03:21.735 --> 00:03:25.343
tsu visn fun ale lagern ver iz geblibn

00:03:25.343 --> 00:03:29.394
ober leyder nokh khadoshim zukhn hot men gezen az

00:03:29.394 --> 00:03:33.194
un m'hot ongehoybn gevoyr vern az vos alts iz geven hot men gevust az

00:03:33.227 --> 00:03:36.241
ir zent geblibn in BERGEN BELSEN?

00:03:33.278 --> 00:03:34.909
s'iz nishto keyn hofenung.

00:03:35.455 --> 00:03:40.210
ikh bin geblibn in BERGEN BELSEN biz ikh bin geforn in KIBUTS ⟨arayn in⟩ a por khadoshim.

00:03:39.623 --> 00:03:41.119
m'iz a por kh-

