00:06:39.118 --> 00:06:42.798
hob ikh nisht gevolt forn, vayl er iz nisht geven azoy frum

00:06:42.798 --> 00:06:43.835
hob ikh moyre gehat

00:06:43.835 --> 00:06:48.364
ts- trots dem alem vos ikh hob nisht gegloybt, az s'vet tsurikkumen dos ales, ober

00:06:48.437 --> 00:06:51.148
tsu a fraye mishpokhe hob ikh nisht gevolt forn

00:06:51.188 --> 00:06:52.515
un m'iz geblibn

00:06:52.791 --> 00:06:58.161
