00:06:58.161 --> 00:06:59.741
un oyfneyen a zhaket

00:06:59.741 --> 00:07:01.546
un far mir un far mayn NICHTE

00:07:01.546 --> 00:07:04.142
ober forn nokh England hob ikh nisht gevolt.

00:07:04.013 --> 00:07:06.237
ir hot gevust demolt az ir vilt

00:07:06.237 --> 00:07:12.005
ir zayt geven a yung meydl, ir hot gevust ir vilt blaybn frum, s'hot ⟨ir im⟩ geshtert dos

00:07:11.067 --> 00:07:12.006
dos hot

00:07:12.265 --> 00:07:15.645
ikh hob nisht gegloybt az s'vet dos zayn dos vos s'iz yetst

00:07:15.645 --> 00:07:19.734
az mayne kinde veln geyn azoy in veg vos mayne eltern hobn gevolt

00:07:20.280 --> 00:07:21.472
nor

00:07:22.086 --> 00:07:25.566
a koyekh vos di eltern hobn arayngegebn

00:07:25.566 --> 00:07:27.186
trots dem bin ikh geven yung

00:07:27.186 --> 00:07:28.627
hob ikh nisht gekent

00:07:29.258 --> 00:07:31.530
geyn in, oyf a andern veg.

00:07:32.245 --> 00:07:35.901
ikh hob gekent hobn besere badingungen geyn bay di tsienistishe

00:07:36.632 --> 00:07:41.368
vos zey hobn gemakht, ober d- ikh hob mikh dokh gehaltn tsvishn di frume IMMER.

