00:07:57.942 --> 00:08:02.327
a MIGRASH in Erets Yisroel, ober undz zenen mir nisht gevezn azoy

00:08:03.430 --> 00:08:05.044
⟨s'heyst⟩

00:08:05.556 --> 00:08:10.865
tsienistishn gayst. di mishpokhe hot gevoynt ale nokh in Poyln.

00:08:11.293 --> 00:08:14.597
veynik. ikh hob gehat a bisl mishpokhe vos zenen geforn nokh

00:08:14.597 --> 00:08:15.978
Yerusholaim

