00:08:39.758 --> 00:08:42.278
Ger hot getsoygn nokh Erets Yisroel

00:08:42.278 --> 00:08:43.788
un dos iz geven mayn

00:08:43.788 --> 00:08:46.893
az di, dortn ken ikh oyfshteln nokh dos

00:08:47.136 --> 00:08:50.437
di por yor vos s'vet nokh undz, nokh aza

00:08:50.460 --> 00:08:53.339
khurbn iz nor tsu forn nokh Erets Yisroel.

